jobs.description:
- Stop wildfly indexer
- Delete fuseki dataset
- Delete stanbol data
- Load new file to stanbol/fuseki
- Restart stanbol/fuseki
- Start wildfly indexer

first parameter is the environment
second parameter is either GIT (deploys the raw ronto.ttl) or GENERATED_FILE (deploys the artifact produced by the merge ontologies task).
jobs.name: Deploy-NexusRE-ontology-DEV
